**Shared module:** `supabase/functions/_shared/syncso-preflight.ts`
- `probeAsset(url, kind, minBytes)` HEAD-check (status, content-length, content-type heuristic).
- `inspectWav(bytes)` returns dur/peakDbFs/leadIn/channels/sampleRate.
- `normalizeWav(bytes, { leadInSec=0.25, minTotalSec=3.0, peakDbFs=-1, forceMono=true })` mono downmix + peak-normalize (capped +12dB) + 0.25s leading silence + tail-pad to ≥3.0s. Pure Deno, no ffmpeg.
- `classifySyncError(msg)` → bucket: `provider_unknown_error | segment_rejected | face_detection | audio_issue | video_issue | timeout | rate_limited | ...`.
- `logSyncDispatch(supabase, row)` best-effort insert into `syncso_dispatch_log` (never throws).

**poll-dialog-shots:**
- Cache namespace bumped `trimmed-v13` → `trimmed-v14`; every per-turn WAV runs through `normalizeWav`.
- DialogShot now carries `audio_dur_sec / audio_lead_in_sec / audio_peak_dbfs`.
- Before every `startSyncTurnJob` call: parallel `probeAsset(video, 50kB) + probeAsset(audio, 5kB)`. On any failure → `prepareShotRetry('preflight_video_*' | 'preflight_audio_*')` + log row with `sync_status='PREFLIGHT_BLOCKED'`.
- Every dispatch (success, deferral, hard fail) writes one `syncso_dispatch_log` row.

**compose-dialog-segments:**
- HEAD-probes master video + every de-duped audio URL before paying Sync.so. Any failure → wallet refund + scene `lip_sync_status='failed'` + log row, returns 422 `preflight_failed`.
- Logs `DISPATCHED` / `DISPATCH_FAILED` rows for analytics.

**Telemetry table** (migration `20260529...syncso_dispatch_log`):
- Columns: scene_id, user_id, engine, job_id, turn_idx, attempt, mode, sync_source_kind, video/audio URL+bytes+content_type, audio_dur_sec/lead_in/peak_dbfs/channels/sample_rate, window_start/end, coords, frame_number, http_status, sync_status, error_class, error_message, meta jsonb.
- Indexed on (scene_id, created_at desc), (error_class, created_at desc), (job_id).
- Grants: `service_role` ALL, `authenticated` SELECT gated by `has_role(uid, 'admin')` RLS policy.

**Not implemented in this stage:** Säule 4 face-validation via Gemini Vision (expensive per-dispatch; deferred). Coords sanity helper `checkCoordsBounds` exists in the shared module but is not yet wired into dispatch.
